// MetaChat: hide native Chrome UI when --metachat-mode is active.
// Uses a configurable command blocklist with allowlist override.
// Default blocklist covers bookmarks/history/downloads/settings etc.
// Allowlist preserves essential operations: reload, devtools, extensions.
// Configure via --metachat-mode-blocklist and --metachat-mode-allowlist.
// Both accept comma-separated IDC command names (e.g. "IDC_PRINT,IDC_SAVE_PAGE").

